    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_A9035690-1D42-0135-644A-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>As an admin, you can create grading schemes for all accounts associated with your account. </p>
<p>Once a grading scheme is created for your account, instructors can link the grading scheme to their courses. However, once a grading scheme has been used to assess a student, you cannot edit the grading scheme.</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Any grading schemes you create in an account are available to use within sub-accounts.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-account" data-step-uuid="033db37e-f099-4911-933d-30145b36421e">
    <h2 id="open-account" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Account</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/949/740/original/167b4d34-2e3f-4046-9aed-39673e67bdab.png" srcset="" alt="Open Account" height="542" width="453">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_a4cf8602-5901-4660-96a3-f78a18568117" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Admin</strong> link [1], then click the name of the account [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_grading" data-step-uuid="149EE633-33EE-4DA2-8FEF-85DD6216C5C3">
    <h2 id="open_grading" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Grading</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/797/274/original/open-grading-.png" srcset="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/797/274/original/open-grading-.png 2.0x, https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/797/274/original_lowres/open-grading-.png" alt="Open Grading" height="312" width="161">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_A9039E20-1D42-0135-644C-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Account Navigation, click the <strong>Grading</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_grading_schemes" data-step-uuid="315a3118-3412-4a53-86d8-908d69435c59">
